@startuml
title Schedule Appointment Sequence Diagram

actor Customer
participant "WhatsApp Bot\n(src/bot.js)" as Bot
participant "Order Helpers\n(src/botHelpers.js)" as Helpers
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders

Customer -> Bot : Select "Manage Orders"
Bot -> Helpers : buildManageOrderPoll(userId)
Helpers -> Orders : getOrdersForUser(phone)
Orders --> Helpers : active orders
Helpers --> Bot : poll options
Bot --> Customer : Show active orders
Customer -> Bot : Select order and choose Reschedule
Bot --> Customer : Request new date
Customer -> Bot : Submit YYYY-MM-DD
Bot --> Customer : Request new time
Customer -> Bot : Submit HH:MM / HH:MM AM-PM
Bot -> Orders : updateOrder(id, scheduledDate, scheduleTime)
Orders --> Bot : updated order
Bot --> Customer : Confirm new appointment details

@enduml
